{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_18","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc 'nl -ba docs/changelog/changelog-2026-06-07.md'","aggregated_output":"     1\t# Changelog 2026-06-07\n     2\t\n     3\t- Fixed `AsyncCache` same-key concurrent loads by tracking per-key in-flight promises.\n     4\t- Kept different keys independent because in-flight state is keyed, not global.\n     5\t- Rejected loads are removed from in-flight state, so later calls retry instead of caching failures.\n     6\t- Added black-box red-team coverage for `clear()` during an in-flight load because stale pending loads must not restore cleared cache state.\n     7\t- Guarded in-flight resolution and cleanup by active promise identity so `clear()` cannot be undone by an older load.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
